OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fsunny at first this evening, and then
OL,7,Fclear spells remaining with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers continuing overnight. Feeling
OL,9,Fquite chilly with winds falling light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FIt will feel rather cold
OL,12,Fwith bright or sunny spells and
OL,13,Fscattered heavy showers through
OL,14,FWednesday.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FStill
OL,17,Fcold with sunny spells and scattered
OL,18,Fheavy showers on Thursday and breezy
OL,19,Fat times. Showers and winds ease
OL,20,Fthrough Friday, then mostly dry and
OL,21,Fbright continuing on through Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
